{"tid":1147272,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[極醜惡] 立法會保安稱秘書處要求填表交代「黃藍」政治立場　拒填後遭針對","createTime":"2019-05-09T18:43:56.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-10T09:23:25.000Z","uid":249885,"like":19,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"ae763526c10b82ca4713b998e77dbb7d49eb422e","tid":1147272,"uid":249885,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-09T18:43:56.000Z","msg":"立法會秘書處陳維安一直強調秘書處工作「政治中立」，然而一名聲稱現職立法會保安員今日在議員陪同下，公開指控秘書處於2017年10月、即取消議員資格（DQ）風波之後，要求她在一份表格上，白紙黑紙交代政治立場，在「黃」及「藍」之間選擇，該名保安員拒絕填寫，其後持續遭針對，更面對情緒問題，最終選擇今月辭職。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n該保安員為黃女士，2016年加入立法會任保安，此前是退休公務員。黃女士形容自己政治中立，故當時拒絕小組上司的要求，未有簽署表格，而當時同組的其餘14名保安同事，均在表格填寫「藍」。<br />\n<br />\n黃女士形容，自己拒絕填寫表格後，一直被針對，包括在立法會附近範圍攙扶一名婆婆，卻被指「擅離職守」；要求拿回績效評估副本時，對方表示「對你無好處」；以及只被指派到較少機會出現議會衝突的地方駐守；回應時任議員助理黃浩銘的打招呼後，被秘書處訓示，稱她「和一些不應該與之談話的人談話」。黃女士指出，自己曾在2018年12月與立法會人事部主管對話，對方再次詢問其政治立場為何。<br />\n<br />\n對於為何選擇在現時公開指控，黃女士稱自己被針對後受精神困擾，需要看精神科醫生，而陳維安日前在立法會稱秘書處辦事是不偏不倚，自己當時身在醫院，看到相關報道感到很感觸，她形容自己是「最低層的員工」，批評陳維安「高高在上，根本不會知道我的壓力，被文字獄欺壓」。<br />\n<br />\n協助該名保安的公民黨譚文豪，批評陳維安領導的秘書處欺凌「不歸邊的人」，是白色恐怖、政治審查，他質疑陳維安是否知悉事件；即使陳維安聲稱不知道，但事態嚴重，陳維安和立法會行政管理委員會亦應全面徹查。譚文豪預告，若行管會拒絕，將尋求動用《立法會（權力及特權）條例》調查。<br />\n<br />\n明報<br />\n<a href=\"https://m.mingpao.com/ins/港聞/article/20190509/s00001/1557386670259/立法會保安稱秘書處要求填表交代「黃藍」政治立場-拒填後遭針對\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%E6%B8%AF%E8%81%9E%2Farticle%2F20190509%2Fs00001%2F1557386670259%2F%E7%AB%8B%E6%B3%95%E6%9C%83%E4%BF%9D%E5%AE%89%E7%A8%B1%E7%A7%98%E6%9B%B8%E8%99%95%E8%A6%81%E6%B1%82%E5%A1%AB%E8%A1%A8%E4%BA%A4%E4%BB%A3%E3%80%8C%E9%BB%83%E8%97%8D%E3%80%8D%E6%94%BF%E6%B2%BB%E7%AB%8B%E5%A0%B4-%E6%8B%92%E5%A1%AB%E5%BE%8C%E9%81%AD%E9%87%9D%E5%B0%8D&d=7bK604G145JEtCxDEZ4NGi3KoYHjImyLH66vjnFGY4M%3D&h=943196eb\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%E6%B8%AF%E8%81%9E%2Farticle%2F20190509%2Fs00001%2F1557386670259%2F%E7%AB%8B%E6%B3%95%E6%9C%83%E4%BF%9D%E5%AE%89%E7%A8%B1%E7%A7%98%E6%9B%B8%E8%99%95%E8%A6%81%E6%B1%82%E5%A1%AB%E8%A1%A8%E4%BA%A4%E4%BB%A3%E3%80%8C%E9%BB%83%E8%97%8D%E3%80%8D%E6%94%BF%E6%B2%BB%E7%AB%8B%E5%A0%B4-%E6%8B%92%E5%A1%AB%E5%BE%8C%E9%81%AD%E9%87%9D%E5%B0%8D&h=d4d5c88f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://m.mingpao.com/ins/港聞/article/20190509/s00001/1557386670259/立法會保安稱秘書處要求填表交代「黃藍」政治立場-拒填後遭針對</a>"},{"pid":"8ddefbdcc7d8aa52c250df931042e393622e8045","tid":1147272,"uid":249885,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-09T18:44:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 政治中立是笑話"},{"pid":"7aaf7499ed4760cce6ffed0027d6301dde507870","tid":1147272,"uid":12265,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8ddefbdcc7d8aa52c250df931042e393622e8045","tid":1147272,"uid":249885,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-09T18:44:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 政治中立是笑話"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-09T18:53:32.000Z","msg":"真係有咁既人既<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1d277a27dfa629a8b5d955acd4e7b758b09e50ea","tid":1147272,"uid":50457,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-09T22:19:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fa1bb25ae99e4eb3a925920c08132420d28230db","tid":1147272,"uid":38216,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-09T23:30:20.000Z","msg":"it&rsquo;s time to pick your side."},{"pid":"ecdd0d493a85badfb5a1a88286bd1c841c761299","tid":1147272,"uid":118988,"like":0,"dislike":14,"score":-14,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-09T23:37:09.000Z","msg":"有無人覺得成件事好鬼？有D 似釘書健單野<br />\n立法會無可能咁明目張膽用「書面形式」問呢D 敏感話題，如果真係有張問卷應該影底做紀錄，或者一早拿住張野公開搞大件事<br />\n點駛咁鬼鼠<br />\n而且立法會保安閒閒地一百幾十人，無理由得佢一個黃絲，點會淨係炒佢<br />\n<br />\n一定係有D 原因比個保安借題發揮"},{"pid":"3ce45e880f5f7a5cf9a7c4354783f246b52ffa60","tid":1147272,"uid":100347,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-09T23:56:11.000Z","msg":"又擠牙膏"},{"pid":"8795bf53a3781ec7be99702223cd1bcd3a6f00fc","tid":1147272,"uid":48234,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-10T00:06:51.000Z","msg":"退休公務員走去做非公務員工作，結果就連跟返一貫做法政治中立都唔得<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">屌你老母呢個撚係立法會?應該正名做垃圾會</span></span>"},{"pid":"873d04dccfa923f165149b50d13e0e9a4f913dcf","tid":1147272,"uid":249885,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-10T03:08:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"92beef8bb27bdd2c2274d1af10cf90cc1271427d","tid":1147272,"uid":249885,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-10T06:30:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1e54129eca2b46905843b365e0a6ceb958c58e08","tid":1147272,"uid":249885,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-10T09:23:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}